        public abstract CancelResult onItemClick(org.bukkit.event.inventory.InventoryClickEvent event,
                                         org.bukkit.entity.Player player,
                                         InventoryProxy inventoryProxy,
                                         org.bukkit.inventory.ItemStack clickedItem)
        You need to complete the event when item clicked. You don't need to worry about the last line if you create the page with preset page. 你需要实现当物品被点击后的方法。 你不必处理最后一行的点击事件如果此界面是你使用预设界面创建的。
        参数:
        event - InventoryClickEvent
        player - Player who clicked the item
        inventoryProxy - The InventoryProxy that response to this inventory
        clickedItem - the item that been clicked
        返回:
        是否需要被取消点击事件 CancelResult
